  "texts": [
    "However, these results were not significant.",
    "GPT-4 showed comparable performance for both frequent and less frequent diseases, but significantly better performance compared to rare (p = 0•0203).",
    "Regarding treatment options, comparing performance of GPT-4 (median, 4•5, IQR = [4•0;4•75]) to GPT-3•5 (median: 4•25 (IQR = [4•0;4•69]) fewer differences were observed.",
    "Results in Fig. 1c indicated superior, however, not significant performance of GPT-4 (p = 0•0503).",
    "Any influence of the diseases' frequency on performance could not be observed."
  ]
